name: "LA PAPESSA"
description:
I withdraw from the worldliness and the din, it is time to enter the self. it takes calm to hatch the egg.

my face is as cold as the room I live in, but the book between my legs is open for him who knows how to approach.
.
.
.This card is part of an original tarot deck made by Rahtattoo. 
The 22 works that compose it are the result of the study of the ancient symbolism that animates the tarot's major arcana.
